	http://code.2x.com/release/linuxterminalserver/src/linuxterminalserver-1.5.0-common-r21-src.tar.gz
	http://code.2x.com/release/linuxterminalserver/src/linuxterminalserver-1.5.0-client-r21-src.tar.gz"

